        name: `Helicopter Tour - Crest of the Blue Ridge AVA Vineyards`,
        sort_time: "2026-05-01 11:00:00",
        end_time_formatted: "2026-05-01 18:00",
        detail: "30 Mile - 15 Minute Flight - $149.00 per person - RESERVATIONS REQUIRED - GET TICKETS HERE \nSoar above Henderson County’s vineyards and Blue Ridge Mountain scenery on an exclusive helicopter tour offered by Souther Williams Vineyard and Scenic Helicopter Tours. Enjoy sweeping aerial views of the region recognized as The Crest of the Blue Ridge AVA, appreciating the patterns of grapevines and the surrounding landscape from a unique perspective. This luxury ride pairs the thrill of flight with the refinement of wine country, creating an elegant start to your Cider, Wine and Dine weekend that emphasizes memorable vistas and sensory delight.\nWhat’s included\n\nA helicopter tour over the vineyards and surrounding Blue Ridge Mountain scenery\nScenic aerial views of the Crest of the Blue Ridge AVA region\nLuxury helicopter ride paired with wine-country sophistication\n\nCheck-in details\nMeeting point: Souther Williams Vineyard, 655 Hoopers Creek Rd, Fletcher, NC 28732 - Arrive 15 minutes before flight\nRestrictions\nWeight Limit 300lbs Per Person\nWeight Limit 500lbs Per Flight\nDisclaimers\nRoute and views may vary by weather and operational conditions.\nCancellations\nCustomers will receive a full refund with 24 hours notice of cancellation. Customers will also receive a full refund in case of operator cancellation due to weather or other unforeseen circumstances. Contact us by phone to cancel or inquire about a cancellation. No-shows will be charged the full price.",
