        end_time_formatted: "2026-05-01 23:59",
        detail: "John Németh is a powerhouse blues and soul vocalist whose journey began in Idaho and took him from fronting regional favorite Fat John & the 3 Slims to sharing stages with legends. After a formative stint with Anson Funderburgh and contributing to Elvin Bishop’s GRAMMY®-nominated The Blues Rolls On, Németh emerged as one of modern blues’ most commanding voices. \n\nA multiple Blues Music Award winner and Billboard Blues chart-topper, his Memphis-based sound blends deep soul, gritty harmonica, and high-energy roots grooves. On stage, Németh delivers a fiery, full-throttle performance that fuses blues tradition with raw, contemporary edge.",
